Upgrade the earrings.  Cougar claw is a cheap alternative (100p each and will give you a 50p earring to sell)<br>
Collar needs to be upgraded.  Spider fur is a bit expensive though.<br>
Upgrade jagged bands to 6 ac, 65 hp rings.  Expensive till you can get more cash.<br>
Upgrade the mask.  Cougar skin is very easy to get and better.  If you can afford it the grotesque aloy one is a good upgrade.  It also will help replace the dex your loosing from the neck.<br>
You can psudo-upgrade the wrists to hero bracer and/or iksar scaled bracer.  Both are ac 9 but have nicer stats that will be usefull against non-casters as well.  Not sure about the truesilver but it wouldn't be a bad upgrade for the ro.<br>
Upgrade the shoulders.  Not really sure what a good option would be though.<br>
A solid weapon for the price is the Centi Warspear.  Off hand I think its like 5 more damage and 2 or 3 faster delay then GB.<br>
<br>
If you really wanna get some cash head up to the owlbear cave in Hollowshade Moores.  Go to the second to last chamber and then into the left branch.  In the back are two 10 min spawns (rest are like 30 seconds), when you enter the one on the left is the rare one.  The rare should be soloable at your level but you can get help if you want.<br>
Anyhow make sure the grimlings take it over (might have to help the wolves take it first) and camp that spawn.  The grimling rare is a no drop haste belt with 10 ac, 4 str and 20 hp.  Its haste is slightly slower then a FBSS, but I think the stats more then make up for it.  After you have that sell off your FBSS for some decient cash.<br>
