For stuff with no upfront purchasing...Head to warsilk woods also for a bracer of scavenging 9ac 5dex 5sta, decent upgrade easy easy kill.  Also get a few friends and head to scarlet desert in luclin, camp the grol baku for the bracer of defense 15ac 3sta 20hps.  Should be a fun time, lots of mobs and decent xp at your level.<br>
